# Always Push Live

After completing any code changes in this project:

1. Verify the build passes (`npm run build`)
2. Commit with a clear message (only when there are changes to commit)
3. Push to `origin/main` on GitHub
4. Deploy to Vercel production: `npx vercel@latest --yes --prod --scope brightbeam-seo`

Do this automatically at the end of tasks unless the user explicitly says not to deploy.

Production URL: https://vezzt.vercel.app
